Package: rde-android
Version: 1.0.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: systemd, dkms
Recommends: rde, android-tools-adb
Maintainer: RDE Team <support@ruizi.store>
Homepage: https://ruizi.store
Description: RDE Android Plugin - Android device management
 ADB connection, Scrcpy screen mirroring and control.
 Runs as an independent plugin via Unix Socket protocol.
 Includes binder kernel module (DKMS) for Android container support.
